          "html": "<style>\n  :root {\n    --color-midnight-grid: #000000;\n    --color-slate-night: #0e0c0c;\n    --color-faded-ash: #aeafb0;\n    --color-ghost-white: #fafaf9;\n    --color-subtle-gray: #e5e7eb;\n    --color-blaze-orange: #f6511d;\n    --font-primary: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  }\n</style>\n<div style=\"background: #0e0c0c; padding: 24px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <div style=\"background: #131111; border: 1px solid rgba(250,250,249,0.12); border-radius: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">\n    <div style=\"padding: 28px 28px 20px 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-blaze-orange); margin-bottom: 14px;\">BLOG</div>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-ghost-white); margin: 0 0 16px 0;\">U.S. Treasury Redesigns Financial Counter-Terrorism Regulation</h2>\n      <p style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-faded-ash); margin: 0 0 20px 0;\">The U.S. Treasury's FinCEN has proposed a rule to redesign AML/CFT regulations to prioritize outcomes over process. New programs will be redesigned around ability to detect and respond to financial crime, instead of volume of paperwork.</p>\n      <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 160px; background: #1a1818; border-radius: 0px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 80%; height: 60%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1c1c 0%, #252222 50%, #1a1818 100%); border-radius: 0px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 3px; background: rgba(250,250,249,0.08); border-radius: 0;\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; border-top: 1px solid rgba(250,250,249,0.12);\">\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; background: transparent; border-right: 1px solid rgba(250,250,249,0.12); transition: background 0.2s;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-ghost-white);\">READ MORE</span>\n        <svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 6h8M7 3l3 3-3 3\" stroke=\"#fafaf9\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-ghost-white);\">VIEW CAREERS</span>\n        <svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 6h8M7 3l3 3-3 3\" stroke=\"#fafaf9\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
