          "html": "<style>\n  :root {\n    --color-midnight-grid: #000000;\n    --color-slate-night: #0e0c0c;\n    --color-faded-ash: #aeafb0;\n    --color-ghost-white: #fafaf9;\n    --color-subtle-gray: #e5e7eb;\n    --color-blaze-orange: #f6511d;\n    --font-primary: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  }\n</style>\n<div style=\"background: #0a0808; padding: 24px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <div style=\"background: #111010; border: 1px solid rgba(250,250,249,0.1); border-radius: 0px; padding: 32px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-blaze-orange); margin-bottom: 12px;\">CAREERS</div>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-ghost-white); margin: 0 0 16px 0;\">Build Resilient Systems</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-faded-ash); margin: 0 0 28px 0;\">We're engineers and operations from a range of disciplines, working to automate companies. If you're drawn to hard problems, we'd like to meet you. We're backed by Kleiner Perkins and First Round, and based in Jackson Square, San Francisco.</p>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(250,250,249,0.12); border-bottom: none; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;\">\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-ghost-white); margin-bottom: 3px;\">Software Engineer</div>\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-faded-ash);\">Full-Time · San Francisco</div>\n        </div>\n        <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4\" stroke=\"#aeafb0\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(250,250,249,0.12); border-bottom: none; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;\">\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-ghost-white); margin-bottom: 3px;\">Research Engineer</div>\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-faded-ash);\">Full-Time · San Francisco</div>\n        </div>\n        <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4\" stroke=\"#aeafb0\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(250,250,249,0.12); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;\">\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-ghost-white); margin-bottom: 3px;\">Product Engineer</div>\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-faded-ash);\">Full-Time · San Francisco</div>\n        </div>\n        <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4\" stroke=\"#aeafb0\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-blaze-orange); text-decoration: none;\">\n      VIEW ALL OPENINGS\n      <svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 6h8M6.5 2.5l3.5 3.5-3.5 3.5\" stroke=\"#f6511d\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
